  "stem": "<p>The expression <math><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi>a</mi><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>/</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow></msup><msup><mi>b</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><mrow><msup><mi>a</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>/</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><msup><mi>b</mi><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>/</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup></mrow></mfrac></math>, where <em>a</em> &gt; 1 and <em>b</em> &gt; 1, is equivalent to which of the following?</p>",
